=== Guinness world distance record ===

A boomerang was used to set a [[Guinness World Records|Guinness World Record]] with a throw of 1,401.5 feet (427.2 meters) by David Schummy on [[Portal:Current events/2005 March 15|March 15, 2005]] at [[Murrarie Recreation Ground]], [[Australia]].&lt;ref&gt;[http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LQ5dW5pHPYk Longest Boomerang Throw]&lt;/ref&gt; This broke the previous record set by Erin Hemmings who threw an [[Aerobie]] 1,333 feet (406.3 meters) on [[July 2003|July 14, 2003]] at [[Fort Funston]], [[San Francisco]].&lt;ref&gt;
