      <text xml:space="preserve">{{For|the calypso performer|Blake Alphonso Higgs}}
{{Infobox musical artist &lt;!-- See Wikipedia:WikiProject_Musicians --&gt;
| Name                = Blind Blake
| Img                 = Blind Blake.jpg
| Img_capt            = The only known photograph of Blind Blake, circa 1927
| Background          = solo_singer&lt;!-- do not tamper --&gt;
| Birth_name          = Arthur Blake
| Born                = ca. 1893
| Died                = 1933?
| Origin              = [[Jacksonville, Florida]], [[United States]] (uncertain)
| Instrument          = [[Guitar]], [[singer|Vocals]]
